snippet.title: Lemmings (PS3) Gameplay
snippet.description: Playing some Lemmings for the PS3, help them get to the goal by using various tools in crazy fun puzzles in a variety of difficulty levels raging from fun to mayhem. (Trial is nothing really, it's just a few simple tutorials to learn the easy tricks and doodads).
